Class DefaultDocumentManagementService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.DefaultDocumentManagementService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DocumentManagementService

    @Named(value="com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.DefaultDocumentManagementService")
public class DefaultDocumentManagementService
extends Object
implements DocumentManagementService

    This service enables you to create, read, update the Document Info Records(DIR) along with object Links.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_DMS_PROCESS_SRV
    API Version:1
    Communication Scenario:Product Lifecycle Management - Master Data Integration (SAP_COM_0105)
    Scope Items:Change Record based Product Data Management (1NF)
